OpenU IL Accordion Topics Course Format
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------
Description
----------------------------------------------------

A Moodle course format "accordion topics" which allows the topics to be minimized and maximized.


----------------------------------------------------
Installation Information
----------------------------------------------------

1. Copy "ouil" directory to moodle/course/format.
2. After you have copied the files you may choose this course format from inside Moodle.



